@startuml UC01_Sequence
title UC01: 用户登录 - 顺序图

actor "用户" as UserActor
boundary "登录界面" as LoginForm
control "登录控制器" as LoginController
entity "用户" as UserEntity

UserActor -> LoginForm : 输入账号密码
LoginForm -> LoginController : 提交登录请求(username, password)
LoginController -> UserEntity : findUser(username)
UserEntity --> LoginController : userObj
LoginController -> UserEntity : validatePassword(password)
UserEntity --> LoginController : boolean

alt 验证通过
    LoginController --> LoginForm : 登录成功
    LoginForm -> UserActor : 进入主页
else 验证失败
    LoginController --> LoginForm : 提示错误信息
    LoginForm -> UserActor : 允许重试
end
@enduml
